               <msContents>
                  <summary>Lines 1-3 contain the last three lines of a page of the codex. For the probable content, see section on content of the electronic version of P. Mich. inv. 21 I. In l. 4 the word synkoptikois may be restored, suggesting that the second recipe might have been concerned with synkope, a sudden loss of strength.</summary>
                  <msItemStruct>
